  "body": "## v0.3.35 (2026-06-09)\n\n### Runtimes Tab: 30-day token usage bar chart\n\nBoss 2026-06-09 requirements:\n1. Top bar chart (30 bars, 1 day each)\n2. Color gradient (darker top for higher usage)\n3. 3 date labels (left/center/right)\n4. Runtime cards auto-adapt height\n\n### Tech\n- Data: /api/dashboard/usage (flexible fallback to /api/usage/daily, mock 30 days)\n- Component: ui/components/TokenBarChart.kt (Compose Canvas)\n- Gradient: Brush.verticalGradient (#2563EB -> #93C5FD)\n- Card: BoxWithConstraints deduct chartHeight = 80.dp\n\n### Also fixed\n- Green title v0.3.33: Repository me() success forces Internal(green)\n- Multi-workspace dropdown + internal/domain/disconnected colors\n- Daemon status detail dialog\n- Task start/end sound (ding=notification, dong=600Hz synth)\n- Default Tab = Agents"
